@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
actor User
participant Frontend as FE
participant "Auth Service" as API
participant "Email Provider" as Email
participant Database as DB

User -> FE: Enter Email & Click "Send OTP"
FE -> API: Request OTP (Email)
API -> DB: Check if User Exists
API -> API: Generate 6-digit OTP
API -> DB: Save OTP Hash & Expiry (e.g. 5 mins)
API -> Email: Send Email with OTP
Email --> User: Deliver OTP Email
API --> FE: Confirm OTP Sent

User -> FE: Enter OTP Code
FE -> API: Verify OTP (Email, Code)
API -> DB: Fetch OTP Hash & Expiry

alt OTP Valid & Not Expired
    API -> API: Delete OTP
    API -> DB: Fetch or Create User Profile
    API -> API: Generate JWT (Access Token)
    API --> FE: Return JWT & User Data
    FE -> FE: Save JWT in LocalStorage
    FE --> User: Login Successful, Redirect to Home
else OTP Invalid or Expired
    API --> FE: Error "Invalid/Expired OTP"
    FE --> User: Show Error Message
end
@enduml
